{"type":"text","timestamp":1784658796650,"sessionID":"ses_07a0c4a02ffeHytxAf8bhFe3RT","part":{"id":"prt_f85f41c43001pVdAEDGgkM2395","messageID":"msg_f85f41a8a001ZCsaBt05eOnuV1","sessionID":"ses_07a0c4a02ffeHytxAf8bhFe3RT","type":"text","text":"Implemented a full project scaffold for **RemixHub**:\n\n- **FastAPI backend** (`backend/app/main.py`) with placeholder routes for trends, content generation, and dispatch.\n- **Dockerfile** for the API container, installing required dependencies.\n- **requirements.txt** covering FastAPI, AI/NLP libraries, Kafka client, PostgreSQL driver, Spark, and auth utilities.\n- **docker‑compose.yml** defining services:\n  - `api` (FastAPI)\n  - `postgres` (PostgreSQL)\n  - `zookeeper` & `kafka` (Confluent platform)\n  - `spark` (Spark master)\n- **README.md** summarizing architecture, core APIs, and quick‑start instructions.\n\nThe scaffold provides a runnable Docker environment and a clear starting point for implementing the behavior‑verified trend engine, AI content generation, and social‑connect dispatcher.","time":{"start":1784658795587,"end":1784658796646}}}
